                  </persName>, <rs id="t18510616-1268-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18510616-1268-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18510616-1268-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>for a like offence: to which</rs>
